maneuvers.narrative: Start out going north toward Akhaura Road.
Turn left onto Akhaura Road (Crossing into বাংলাদেশ).
Enter next roundabout and take the 1st exit onto N2/Dhaka - Sylhet Highway.
Dhaka-Sylhet becomes N2/Dhaka-Sylhet Highway. Pass through 1 roundabout.
Enter next roundabout and take the 1st exit onto R301.
Turn slight right onto N302/Ashulia Highway.
Take the Daulatdia Ferry crossing Ferry (Check schedule/fares).
Go southeast on Dhaka - Faridpur Hwy.
N702/Jessore - Magura Hwy becomes Khajura Rd.
Turn left to stay on N7/Jessore - Jenaidah Hwy.
Turn left onto N7/Jessore City Bypass.
Enter next roundabout and take the 1st exit onto N706.
N706 becomes NH112 (Crossing into भारत गणराज्य India).
Turn left to stay on NH112.
Take the NH12 exit on the left.
Enter next roundabout and take the 3rd exit onto NH18/NH49.
Turn left to stay on NH49.
Stay straight to go onto NH53. Pass through 3 roundabouts.
Stay straight to go onto SH7.
Turn slight left to stay on SH7.
Turn left to stay on NH53.
Stay straight to go onto NH53.
Stay straight to go onto NH60.
Enter next roundabout and take the 4th exit onto NH160.
Turn slight right onto Agra Rd.
Turn slight left onto Kalyan-Shil Road.
Turn slight left onto Haji Malang Road.
Haji Malang Road becomes Hazi Malang Road.
Turn slight left onto SH43/Pipeline Rd.
